      <p>We only share your information with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The specialist doctor assigned to review your case</li>
        <li>Payment processors (Paymob) to process transactions</li>
        <li>Legal authorities when required by Egyptian law</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We <strong>NEVER</strong>:</p>
